Collections - Manipulation of Data (Store and Manipulate Data)

Collections - Interface - List, Set, Map, Queue
-------------------------------------------------------------
List (Interface) - Implementing class - ArrayList, LinkedList,  -------Vector, Stack

Arraylist - Dynamic Array (Resizing) - Duplicate Allowed - Insertion Order Maintained - Null Allowed

LinkedList - Doubly Linked List - Duplicate Allowed - Insertion Order Maintained - Null Allowed


---------------------------------------------------------
Set (Interface) - Implementing class - HashSet, LinkedHashSet, TreeSet

Set - No Duplicate Allowed - No Insertion Order Maintained - One Null Allowed (Except TreeSet)

HashSet - Hashing Algorithm - No Insertion Order Maintained - One Null Allowed
LinkedHashSet - Hashing Algorithm + Linked List - Insertion Order Maintained - One Null Allowed
TreeSet - Sorting - Red-Black Tree - No Insertion Order Maintained - No Null Allowed